<p><b>Human Rights Council 
Nineteenth session 
</b></p>
<p>Agenda item 3 
</p>
<p><b>Promotion and protection of all human rights, civil,  
</b></p>
<p><b>political, economic, social and cultural rights,  
</b></p>
<p><b>including the right to development  
</b></p>
<p><b>  Report of the Special Rapporteur on the promotion and 
protection of human rights and fundamental freedoms while 
countering terrorism, Ben Emmerson 
</b></p>
<p><b>  Note by the Secretariat 
</b></p>
<p> In its resolution 15/15, the Human Rights Council requested the Special Rapporteur 
</p>
<p>on the promotion and protection of human rights and fundamental freedoms while 
</p>
<p>countering terrorism to report regularly to the Council. The next report of the Special 
</p>
<p>Rapporteur will be submitted to the twentieth session of the Council. 
</p>
